data.description: Welcome to your new home in the charming Park Forest community of Alabaster, Alabama. This 3-bedroom, two-and-a-half-bath residence offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. As you step through the inviting entryway, you are greeted by a spacious and light-filled living area, featuring large windows that showcase the natural beauty of the surrounding Park Forest neighborhood. The well-appointed kitchen boasts sleek countertops, appliances, and ample cabinet space, making it a chef's delight. The adjacent dining area provides a cozy spot for family meals or intimate gatherings. You will find the master bedroom on the main level with a en-suite bath. Upstairs you have 2 generously sized bedrooms with a shared full bath. In the basement you will find room for expansion with plumbing stubbed for a future bath. Set up your showing today to see what Alabaster and Park forest can offer you.
